那么现在我们最后听一遍对话，回顾一下我们刚学的内容。

251
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:56,800
Okay.
好的。

252
00:11:56,800 --> 00:12:01,200
So if we could dim the lights, Jonathan, we can kick off with the first TV advert.
所以如果我们能把灯光调暗一点，乔纳森，我们就可以开始播放第一支电视广告了。

253
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:04,160
Please note that we're still in the early days with this advert, so it might seem a
请注意，这支广告还处于早期阶段，所以可能看起来有点

254
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:06,000
bit rough around the edges.
粗糙。

255
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,000
Okay.
好的。

256
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:10,880
So I just need to click this and the advert should pop up on the screen.
所以我只需要点一下这个，广告就会出现在屏幕上。

257
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:11,880
Hmm.
嗯。

258
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,840
Sorry about this.
抱歉。

259
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,240
Bear with me a second.
请稍等一下。

260
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:18,320
There seems to be a problem with the projector.
投影仪好像有问题。

261
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,320
Let me see.
让我看看。

262
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:27,600
Jonathan, could you lend a hand a second?
乔纳森，你能过来帮个忙吗？

263
