And actually, these type of problems occur very, very often, specifically with the laptop
实际上，这类问题非常非常常见，特别是笔记本电脑

287
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,320
and the projector.
和投影仪之间。

288
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:36,720
And sometimes it doesn't work.
有时候就是不行。

289
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:38,720
It doesn't recognize it.
它识别不了。

290
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,920
And so this is a nice way of handling it.
所以这是一个很好的处理方式。

291
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:41,920
This is.
就是这样。

